<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Reset Your Password - LearnHub</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');
    
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      background: #ffffff;
      margin: 20px auto;
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    }
    
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5 0%, #7c3aed 100%);
      padding: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      color: white;
    }
    
    .logo {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    
    .logo-icon {
      font-size: 32px;
    }
    
    .header h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 15px 0 5px 0;
    }
    
    .header p {
      font-size: 16px;
      opacity: 0.9;
      font-weight: 300;
    }
    
    .content {
      padding: 40px;
    }
    
    .greeting {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #374151;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    
    .message {
      color: #6b7280;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    .reset-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5 0%, #7c3aed 100%);
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 16px 32px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 25px 0;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.3);
    }
    
    .reset-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.4);
    }
    
    .security-note {
      background: #f9fafb;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    
    .security-note h3 {
      color: #374151;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    
    .security-note p {
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    
    .support {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    
    .support p {
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    
    .support-contact {
      color: #4f46e5;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    
    .footer {
      background: #f9fafb;
      padding: 25px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    
    .footer p {
      color: #9ca3af;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    
    .footer-links {
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
    
    .footer-link {
      color: #6b7280;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin: 0 10px;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .footer-link:hover {
      color: #4f46e5;
    }
    
    .expiry-note {
      background: #fffbeb;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #92400e;
    }
    
    .expiry-note strong {
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .container {
        margin: 10px;
        border-radius: 16px;
      }
      
      .header {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      
      .content {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      
      .reset-btn {
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">
        <span class="logo-icon">üìö</span>
        LearnHub Academy
      </div>
      <h1>Password Reset Request</h1>
      <p>Secure access to your learning journey</p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="content">
      <p class="greeting">Hello there,</p>
      
      <p class="message">
        We received a request to reset your password for your LearnHub account. 
        If this was you, click the button below to create a new secure password 
        and regain access to your courses and learning materials.
      </p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{resetLink}}" class="reset-btn">Reset My Password</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="expiry-note">
        <strong>‚è∞ Important:</strong> This password reset link will expire in 1 hour 
        for your security.
      </div>
      
      <div class="security-note">
        <h3>üîí Security Alert</h3>
        <p>
          If you didn't request this password reset, please ignore this email. 
          Your account remains secure. We recommend enabling two-factor authentication 
          for added protection.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="support">
        <p>
          Need help? Our support team is here for you. Contact us at 
          <a href="mailto:support@learnhub.com" class="support-contact">support@learnhub.com</a> 
          or visit our help center.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
      <p>¬© 2025 LearnHub Academy. Empowering learners worldwide.</p>
      <p>This email was sent to {{email}} because you're registered with LearnHub.</p>
      
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="#" class="footer-link">Privacy Policy</a>
        <a href="#" class="footer-link">Terms of Service</a>
        <a href="#" class="footer-link">Unsubscribe</a>
        <a href="#" class="footer-link">Help Center</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>